### Current User
GET {{host}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
Authorization: Token {{auth_token}}

### Update User
PUT {{host}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
Authorization: Token {{auth_token}}

{
  "user": {
    "email": {{user.email}}
  }
}